00:02:07.390 --> 00:02:12.200
In 2010, he was on the run from locals trying
to chase him off his land to develop it.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.280
His huts were bulldozed, and he was alone.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:17.920
He killed an encroaching man by shooting an
